      "content": "hey i'm looking at moving my emergency fund out of my checking account to a high yield savings account. i have $15,000 saved right now. i found three different rates: 4.2%, 4.5%, and 4.8% APY. can you show me how much interest i'd actually make in a year for each of those if i don't add any more money?",
